    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been a total joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape, runs smoothly, and has been really well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how well it handles! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
