    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque through a precision-gated 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, supported by a factory-spec multi-link rear suspension and refreshed bushings. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal remains dry. Recent diagnostics show healthy fuel trims and no bore scoring. This is a mechanically sorted specimen with a crisp throttle response and a flat cornering profile, optimized for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
