    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 premium performance SUV has been my pride and joy, and it shows in its well-documented history. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Charcoal Metallic that retains a deep luster. Upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a vehicle of this age but nothing that detracts from its overall presence. The alloy wheels are clean with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of black leather and brushed aluminum. The seats are firm and supportive; the driver\u2019s seat shows light softening of the leather on the entry bolster, but there are no tears or stains. All interior electronics, from the premium surround-sound system to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, having followed a strict maintenance schedule at the dealership. The transmission shifts crisply, and the tires were replaced last season, offering excellent grip. This vehicle offers a perfect blend of reliability and luxury for the discerning driver who appreciates a car that has been cared for properly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
