    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This 3.2L atmospheric straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under load. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with an upgraded water pump. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension kinematics remain sharp, providing the communicative feedback this chassis is legendary for. A driver-spec example optimized for peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
